NIIT-StackRoute 2017-18.
Exercise
Define mongoose schema for data model for online Blogging app
User registers and blogs
Each blogs gets a unique link to it
Blogs have editable comments & replies
Blogs have tags, votes, shares, citations
Other uses can bookmark blogs
Author is shown details of number reads, views etc., on a date-time scale
Create DAO module for the same in TDD way, to test both positive and
negative scenarios along with scenarios like no data, normal data,
large data, database is down etc.,
